msgid ""
"Here you can discover and configure SMS providers to send transactional "
"messages, including order confirmations, shipping updates, and delivery "
"notifications."
msgstr ""
"Di sini Anda dapat menemukan dan mengonfigurasi penyedia SMS untuk mengirim "
"pesan transaksional, termasuk konfirmasi pesanan, pembaruan pengiriman, dan "
"pemberitahuan pengiriman."

